187class CreateNewPage {
188public:
189 using Arguments = std::tuple<const WebKit::FrameInfoData&, const WebKit::WebPageProxyIdentifier&, const WebCore::ResourceRequest&, const WebCore::WindowFeatures&, const WebKit::NavigationActionData&>;
190
191 static IPC::MessageName name() { return IPC::MessageName::WebPageProxy_CreateNewPage; }
192 static constexpr bool isSync = true;
193
194 using DelayedReply = CreateNewPageDelayedReply;
195 static constexpr auto callbackThread = WTF::CompletionHandlerCallThread::ConstructionThread;
196 static void send(UniqueRef<IPC::Encoder>&&, IPC::Connection&, const std::optional<WebCore::PageIdentifier>& newPageID, const std::optional<WebKit::WebPageCreationParameters>& newPageParameters);
197 using Reply = std::tuple<std::optional<WebCore::PageIdentifier>&, std::optional<WebKit::WebPageCreationParameters>&>;
198 using ReplyArguments = std::tuple<std::optional<WebCore::PageIdentifier>, std::optional<WebKit::WebPageCreationParameters>>;
199 CreateNewPage(const WebKit::FrameInfoData& originatingFrameInfoData, const WebKit::WebPageProxyIdentifier& originatingPageID, const WebCore::ResourceRequest& request, const WebCore::WindowFeatures& windowFeatures, const WebKit::NavigationActionData& navigationActionData)
200 : m_arguments(originatingFrameInfoData, originatingPageID, request, windowFeatures, navigationActionData)
201 {
202 }
203
204 const Arguments& arguments() const
205 {
206 return m_arguments;
207 }
208
209private:
210 Arguments m_arguments;
211};
